@startuml
title TPL Conceptual Domain - Identity and Access

hide methods
hide stereotypes
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
left to right direction

class User
class Person
class PersonTeam
class Role
class Permission

Person "0..1" -- "1" User : represents >
PersonTeam "*" -- "*" Person : members
User "*" -- "*" Role : has >
Role "*" -- "*" Permission : grants >

note right of Permission
Permissions are intent-level rights.
View and edit rights are separated
by business domain.
end note

@enduml
